{"tid":2071500,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蓬佩奧稱香港9月選舉將可了解中共尊重香港自由意向","createTime":"2020-06-20T01:31:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-20T02:05:54.000Z","uid":18569,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b3a6bdacfc3504fa3f8d3c2c1632a64969d36ffa","tid":2071500,"uid":18569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T01:31:11.000Z","msg":"蓬佩奧稱香港9月選舉將可了解中共尊重香港自由意向<br />\n<br />\n美國國務卿蓬佩奧表示，如果中國將香港視為內地的其中一個城市，例如深圳和上海，美國將一視同仁，不會視香港為享有自治的城市，並放棄任何美國和香港之間訂立獨特協議。蓬佩奧在哥本哈根民主高峰會的視像會議表示，關注香港9月舉行的選舉，認為將令外界了解，中共在尊重香港自由方面的意向，又說華盛頓正展開程序，決定那些人要對遏制香港的自由負責。<br />\n<br />\n2020-06-20 09:25:11<br />\n美國識玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c4b0c39339dd2096c1f02e6c570ec68b5bdb215","tid":2071500,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T01:42:12.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb2214f6fe809035bd68656f00ccd9c376b56b3d","tid":2071500,"uid":152976,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T01:46:09.000Z","msg":"仲對共匪抱有幻想 我都唔知話佢識玩定唔識玩好"},{"pid":"e9ce692a0260ac5a01a397d9b3e329c01aa9890a","tid":2071500,"uid":1441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T01:46:57.000Z","msg":"仲要等9月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7250c784d8cca6c44574d9d0e48fe75bb0db662","tid":2071500,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T01:59:23.000Z","msg":"5毛， 分化， 熱狗32+冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb3bff1303d44c2daf477a0846118559b810bafb","tid":2071500,"uid":179409,"like":3,"dislike":0,"sco